WEBVTT

00:03.335 --> 00:04.842
Hey. I'm gonna be
working late tonight,

00:04.910 --> 00:06.735
so don't wait up.

00:06.803 --> 00:08.872
Are those scones?
Easy, Debbie drive-thru.

00:08.940 --> 00:11.276
Sit down and eat
with your sister.

00:11.344 --> 00:12.711
Do you remember her?

00:12.779 --> 00:14.345
The one who bakes you
goodies every day?

00:14.413 --> 00:16.280
Yeah, sounds
vaguely familiar,

00:16.347 --> 00:17.885
but I am so late.

00:17.953 --> 00:19.455
Oh, well,
then I'll drive you.

00:19.523 --> 00:20.957
- Uh...
- Come on.

00:21.025 --> 00:22.497
I am seriously overdue
for some Annie time.

00:22.565 --> 00:24.133
Annie time
is pretty awesome,

00:24.201 --> 00:26.400
but I need my car
because I have a thing tonight.

00:26.468 --> 00:28.102
I thought you said
you were working late.

00:28.170 --> 00:29.703
Yeah, that "Thing"
is an acquisitions conference

00:29.771 --> 00:31.303
in Arlington.
I know.

00:31.371 --> 00:32.805
Thrilling stuff,
right?

00:32.872 --> 00:34.738
You know, you've been working
past 10:00 for weeks now.

00:34.806 --> 00:36.504
Is everything okay?

00:36.572 --> 00:39.972
Yeah, it's fine.
Have a great day.

